oked like I was talking down to the guild. In my opinion there is nothing that can be said to tarnish the guild name or stature. For the MIGHTY AEGIS WOLVES of the Tunare and other severs, are seen for the actions and representation in game. I have wronged a few of the people in the guild, which I will now apologize.<br>
<br>
<br>
