<br>
<br>
     As for my retaging I am going to put the thoughts on it off for a bit an do my own thing. I would love to group, hunt, quest with any wolf old or new. I will treat you all as my brothers and sisters because in my eyes your are. Just because I do not carry a Guild tag does not make me less of a person. If by chance things work out I would like to be given a Lone Wolf quest. As in my eyes it would allow me to take a less political part in the guild. Not that I had one but I hope that can be understood. <br>
<br>
